  "texts": [
    "This paper delved into the significance of tailored evaluation metrics specifically for healthcare chatbots.",
    "We introduced a comprehensive set of user-centered evaluation metrics, grouped into four categories: accuracy, trustworthiness, empathy, and computing performance.",
    "The study highlighted the potential impact of confounding variables on metric definition and evaluation.",
    "Additionally, we emphasized how these metrics can address pertinent issues and enhance the reliability and quality of healthcare chatbot systems, ultimately leading to an improved patient experience.",
    "Lastly, we examined the challenges associated with developing and implementing these metrics in the evaluation process."
